clinicalDescription: Overview: A general feeling of discomfort, illness, or lack of well-being. Scores of illnesses or disorders (and medicines) can lead to different degrees of malaisePresentation: Might have fatigue, pain, and a lack of interest in usual activitiesAssessment: Physical exam Plan: Treatment based on exam and tests. Prognosis: Not a disease, need to look for other symptoms to reach a diagnosis.
